[package]
name = "MFEKmath"
version = "0.1.2"
authors = [ "Matthew Blanchard <matthewrblanchard@gmail.com>", "Fredrick R. Brennan <copypasteⒶkittens.ph>", "MFEK Authors",]
edition = "2018"
license = "Apache-2.0"
description = "A library which supplies mathematics and algorithms for manipulating beziers."

[dependencies]
flo_curves = "0.6"
xmltree = "0.10"
plist = "1.3"
log = "0.4"

[features]
default = [ "skia-safe", "glifparser/skia", "glifparser/mfek",]
fontforge = [ "fontforge-typeconv",]
strict = []
skia = [ "skia-safe", "glifparser/skia",]

[dependencies.skia-safe]
version = ">0.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.kurbo]
git = "https://github.com/MFEK/kurbo.rlib"
branch = "master"

[dependencies.spline]
git = "https://github.com/MFEK/spline.rlib"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.glifparser]
git = "https://github.com/MFEK/glifparser.rlib"
features = [ "glifserde",]
branch = "master"
default-features = false

[dependencies.fontforge-typeconv]
git = "https://github.com/MFEK/fontforge-typeconv.rlib"
branch = "main"
default-features = false
optional = true

[package]
name = "chrono_locale"
version = "0.1.1"
authors = [ "Alessandro Pellizzari <alex@amiran.it>",]
description = "Localised date and time formatting library for Rust, based on chrono"
homepage = "https://github.com/Alex-PK/chrono-locale"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "date", "time", "calendar",]
categories = [ "date-and-time",]
license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/Alex-PK/chrono-locale"
build = "build.rs"

[dependencies]
chrono = "0.4"
lazy_static = "1.2"

[build-dependencies]
serde = "1"
serde_json = "1"
serde_derive = "1"
walkdir = "2"

[dependencies.num-integer]
version = "0.1"
default-features = false

[package]
name = "glifparser"
version = "2.0.1"
authors = [ "Fredrick Brennan <copypaste@kittens.ph>", "MFEK Authors",]
edition = "2021"
license = "Apache-2.0"
keywords = [ "glif", "parsers", "ufo-format", "fonts",]
description = "A parser and writer for UFO `.glif` files"
repository = "https://github.com/MFEK/glifparser.rlib"

[dependencies]
derive_more = "0.99"
derivative = "2.2"
log = "0.4"
trees = "0.4"
plist = "1.3"
itertools = "0.10"
float-cmp = "0.9"
dyn-clone = "1.0.9"
spline = "0.2.0"

[dev-dependencies]
env_logger = "0.9"
test-log = "0.2"
lazy_static = "1"

[features]
glifimage = [ "image",]
glifserde = [ "serde", "kurbo/serde", "integer_or_float/serde", "plist/default",]
default = [ "glifimage", "glifserde",]
skia = [ "default", "skia-safe",]
mfek = [ "default",]
more-image-formats = [ "image/gif", "image/jpeg", "image/webp", "image/bmp", "image/tiff",]
more-iof = [ "integer_or_float/num-traits",]
fat = [ "glifimage", "glifserde", "skia", "mfek", "more-image-formats", "more-iof",]
fat-no-skia = [ "glifimage", "glifserde", "mfek", "more-image-formats", "more-iof",]

[dependencies.xmltree]
version = "0.10"
features = [ "attribute-order",]

[dependencies.kurbo]
git = "https://github.com/MFEK/kurbo.rlib"
branch = "master"

[dependencies.skia-safe]
version = ">0.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.image]
version = "0.24"
features = [ "png",]
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]
optional = true

[dependencies.flo_curves]
version = "0.6"
optional = true

[dependencies.integer_or_float]
version = "0.3"
default-features = false
features = [ "hash", "float-cmp", "more-serde", "faster-strconv",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "fat-no-skia",]

[package]
name = "glifrenderer"
version = "0.1.2"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
skia-safe = ">0.53.0"
log = "0.4"
font-kit = "0.10"
derive_more = "0.99"
enum-unitary = "0.4.3"
enum-iterator = "0.7.0"
lazy_static = "1.4"
kurbo = "0.8"
flo_curves = "0.6"
num-traits = "0.2"

[dependencies.glifparser]
git = "https://github.com/MFEK/glifparser.rlib"
branch = "master"
features = [ "mfek", "skia",]

[dependencies.MFEKmath]
git = "https://github.com/MFEK/math.rlib"
branch = "main"
features = [ "skia",]

[package]
name = "kurbo"
version = "0.9.5"
authors = [ "Raph Levien <raph.levien@gmail.com>",]
license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"
edition = "2021"
keywords = [ "graphics", "curve", "curves", "bezier", "geometry",]
repository = "https://github.com/linebender/kurbo"
description = "A 2D curves library"
readme = "README.md"
categories = [ "graphics",]

[features]
default = [ "std",]
std = []

[dependencies]
smallvec = "1.10"

[dev-dependencies]
rand = "0.8.0"

[dependencies.arrayvec]
version = "0.7.1"
default-features = false

[dependencies.libm]
version = "0.2.6"
optional = true

[dependencies.mint]
version = "0.5.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.schemars]
version = "0.8.6"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.105"
optional = true
default-features = false
features = [ "alloc", "derive",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "mint", "schemars", "serde",]

[target."cfg(target_arch=\"wasm32\")".dev-dependencies.getrandom]
version = "0.2.0"
features = [ "js",]

[package]
name = "mfek-ipc"
version = "0.0.4-beta1"
authors = [ "Fredrick Brennan <copypaste@kittens.ph>",]
description = "Modular Font Editor K (MFEK) inter-process communication library."
edition = "2018"
license = "Apache-2.0"
keywords = [ "mfek-ipc",]
repository = "https://github.com/MFEK/ipc.rlib"

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
notify = "5"
serde_json = "1.0"
serde = "1.0"
figlet-rs = "0.1"
colored = "2"
atty = "0.2"
chrono = "0.4"

[dev-dependencies]
env_logger = "0.10"
test-log = "0.2"

[features]
reproducible-build = []

[dependencies.glifparser]
git = "https://github.com/MFEK/glifparser.rlib"
branch = "master"

[dependencies.chrono_locale]
version = "0.1"
git = "https://github.com/MFEK/chrono-locale.rlib"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
ansi_term = "0.12"

[package]
name = "nfd"
version = "0.0.4"
authors = [ "Saurav Sachidanand <sauravsachidanand@gmail.com>", "Daniel Collin <daniel@collin.com>", "Denis Kolodin <deniskolodin@gmail.com>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://www.github.com/saurvs/nfd-rs"
description = "Rust bindings to nativefiledialog"
keywords = [ "file", "dialog", "ui",]
build = "build.rs"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0.79"

[package]
name = "pub-mod"
version = "0.1.1"
authors = [ "Fredrick Brennan <copypaste@kittens.ph>",]
edition = "2018"

[dependencies]
syn = "1.0"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[[example]]
name = "json"
required-features = [ "serde",]

[package]
name = "spline"
version = "0.3.0"
license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"
authors = [ "Raph Levien <raph.levien@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
keywords = [ "graphics", "curve", "curves", "bezier", "spline",]
repository = "https://github.com/linebender/spline"
description = "A spline for interactive 2D curve design"
readme = "README.md"
categories = [ "graphics",]

[dev-dependencies]
rand = "0.7"
serde_json = "1.0.59"

[features]
serde = [ "serde_", "kurbo/serde",]

[dependencies.kurbo]
git = "https://github.com/MFEK/kurbo.rlib"
branch = "master"

[dependencies.serde_]
version = "1.0.117"
package = "serde"
features = [ "derive",]
optional = true

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source."https://github.com/mfek/math.rlib"]
git = "https://github.com/mfek/math.rlib"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "main"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/mfek/chrono-locale.rlib"]
git = "https://github.com/mfek/chrono-locale.rlib"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/mfek/glifparser.rlib"]
git = "https://github.com/mfek/glifparser.rlib"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "master"

[source."https://github.com/mfek/glifrenderer.rlib"]
git = "https://github.com/mfek/glifrenderer.rlib"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/mfek/kurbo.rlib"]
git = "https://github.com/mfek/kurbo.rlib"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "master"

[source."https://github.com/mfek/ipc.rlib"]
git = "https://github.com/mfek/ipc.rlib"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/mfek/nfd.rs"]
git = "https://github.com/mfek/nfd.rs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/mfek/pub_mod.rlib"]
git = "https://github.com/mfek/pub_mod.rlib"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/mfek/spline.rlib"]
git = "https://github.com/mfek/spline.rlib"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
